<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Results-Driven Marketing — Olivia Arkema</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Results-driven marketing services tailored to your goals. Mix of digital, traditional, and creative strategies to reach more customers, build awareness, and boost sales." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://oliviaarkema.com/services/marketing" />
    <link rel="icon" href="green_bow.png" />

  <!-- Noto Serif -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    /* ===== Minimal design tokens ===== */
    :root{
      --bg:#faf7f2; --ink:#393831; --muted:#9e9383;
      --blue:#5f849c; --deep:#23424c; --wash:#dae4eb;
      --measure:72ch; --radius:14px;
    }
    /* ===== Base ===== */
    html,body{margin:0;padding:0}
    body{
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--ink);
      font:16px/1.75 'Noto Serif', serif;
      text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;
    }
    a{color:var(--deep); text-decoration:none}
    a:hover{text-decoration:underline}

    /* ===== Layout ===== */
    .wrap{max-width:960px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 20px}
    main{padding:3rem 0 4rem}

    /* Header */
    header.site{padding:14px 0; background:#fff; border-bottom:1px solid #e8e4de; position:sticky; top:0; z-index:10}
    .brand{font-weight:700; color:var(--deep); font-size:20px}
    .site-row{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; }
    .site-links{ display:flex; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .nav-toggle{ display:none; background:none; border:0; color:var(--muted); }
    @media (max-width:760px){
      .nav-toggle{ display:inline-flex; }
      .site-links{
        display:none; position:absolute; right:20px; top:calc(100% + 8px);
        background:#fff; border:1px solid #e8e4de; border-radius:12px; padding:10px;
        box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.08); width:calc(100% - 40px); max-width:440px;
        flex-direction:column; gap:10px;
      }
      .site-links.open{ display:flex; }
    }

    /* ===== Writing surface ===== */
    .letter{max-width:var(--measure); margin:0 auto}
    .lede{font-size:1.125rem; color:var(--muted); margin:.25rem 0 1rem}
    .meta{color:var(--muted); font-size:.95rem; margin:.25rem 0 1.5rem}

    /* Headings */
    h1,h2,h3{line-height:1.2; margin:0 0 .6rem}
    h1{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px); color:var(--deep)}
    h2{font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px); color:var(--blue); margin-top:2.25rem}
    h3{font-size:clamp(18px,2.2vw,22px); color:var(--deep); margin-top:1.75rem}
    p{margin:0 0 1rem}

    /* Blocks */
    .hr{height:1px; background:rgba(95,132,156,.25); margin:2rem 0}
    .callout{ background:#fff; border:2px solid var(--blue); border-radius:var(--radius);
      padding:1rem; margin:1.25rem 0; }
    blockquote{ margin:1.5rem 0; padding:.75rem 1rem; border-left:4px solid var(--blue);
      background:#fff; border-radius:8px; color:var(--deep); }
    figure{margin:1.25rem 0}
    figure img{display:block; width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:10px; border:2px solid var(--blue)}
    figcaption{font-size:.9rem; color:var(--muted); margin-top:.5rem; text-align:center}

    ul,ol{padding-left:1.2rem; margin:0 0 1rem}
    .cta{display:inline-block; background:var(--blue); color:#fff; padding:.7rem 1rem; border-radius:10px}
    .cta:hover{filter:brightness(.95)}

    /* Optional two-column flow on very wide screens */
    @media (min-width:1100px){
      .columns{column-count:2; column-gap:32px}
      .columns > *{break-inside:avoid}
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer.site{padding:28px 0; background:#393831; color:#9e9383}
    footer.site a{color:#9e9383}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="site">
    <div class="wrap site-row">
      <a class="brand" href="/">OA</a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Open menu" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="site-menu">
        <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M4 7h16M4 12h16M4 17h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <nav id="site-menu" class="site-links">
        <a href="/#services">Services</a>
        <a href="/#featuredwork">Work</a>
        <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <article class="wrap letter">
      <!-- Title & lede -->
      <p class="meta">Marketing Services</p>
      <h1>Results-Driven Marketing</h1>
      <p class="lede">No matter your business goals, the right marketing strategy helps you reach more customers, increase brand awareness, and boost sales. I offer a mix of digital, traditional, and creative solutions tailored to your needs.</p>

      <!-- Feature image -->
      <figure>
        <img src="marketing.jpg" alt="Marketing Strategy" />
        <figcaption>Strategy first. Right channels, right message.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <div class="hr"></div>

      <!-- Long-form content -->
      <section class="body">
        <h2>What marketing strategy is best for your business?</h2>
        <p>The best strategy depends on your goals, audience, and budget. Some channels deliver quick wins; others compound over time. We’ll choose the mix that aligns with where you are—and where you’re going.</p>

        <h3>Quick results</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>PPC advertising</strong> to capture high-intent searches.</li>
          <li><strong>Email marketing</strong> to drive immediate traffic and conversions.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Long-term growth</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Content marketing</strong> to build authority.</li>
          <li><strong>SEO</strong> to attract a steady stream of organic traffic.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Engagement & brand</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Social media</strong> for ongoing visibility and community.</li>
          <li><strong>Traditional & local</strong> (direct mail, billboards) when geography matters.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>When word-of-mouth is your edge</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Events & PR</strong> to spark conversation and trust.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Mobile-first moments</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>SMS & in-app</strong> messages for timely, high-attention touchpoints.</li>
        </ul>

        <blockquote>“The key is finding a mix of strategies that align with your audience and business objectives.”</blockquote>

        <p>Not sure where to start? I’ll help you narrow to the 1–3 channels that match your timeline and goals, then test, learn, and iterate.</p>

        <p><a class="cta" href="/contact">Get in Touch</a></p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>

  <footer class="site">
    <div class="wrap" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <small>© <span id="year"></span> Olivia Arkema</small>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px"><a href="/privacy">Privacy</a><a href="/terms">Terms</a></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    const toggle = document.querySelector('.nav-toggle');
    const menu = document.getElementById('site-menu');
    if (toggle && menu){
      toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const isOpen = menu.classList.toggle('open');
        toggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(isOpen));
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
